data.description: Come see this spacious 3 bedroom (potential 4th) 2 bath home located in the awesome town of Centralia MO.  Home has had numerous upgrades including new electrical ran, newer painted rooms inside, new front and back doors, new flooring and light fixtures in main living areas.  Kitchen features new back splash and less than a year old microwave and dishwasher.  Home has a huge yard with room to add a shed/shop/bigger garage out back!  Call for your showing today! 2023-12-02
